25}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's eastern boroughs\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a poll conducted ten years after the Games, two-thirds of London adultsagreedthat hosting the Olympics had left a positive legacy.\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4819, \"end\": 4825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999731858686393, \"rank\": 2.615953043685203e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a poll\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4767}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"two-thirds\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4851, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive legacy\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has now reformed its host bidding process by creating a less public campaign for prospective host cities.\", \"from\": 4893, \"to\": 5006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4897, \"end\": 4900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6046180197806674e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its host bidding process\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 4942}, {\"ngram\": \"a less public campaign\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4977}, {\"ngram\": \"prospective host cities\", \"from\": 4982, \"to\": 5005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, Brisbane won theright to host the 2032 Gameshaving been the first city to go through this new process.\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5016, \"end\": 5024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999996052793, \"